Check-Host Firefox extension
http://check-host.net/

DESCRIPTION
    Check availability of hosts, DNS records, IP addresses from different
    locations. All check are performed with http://check-host.net/

    It allows to check:
     - host information;
     - HTTP service availability;
     - TCP port access;
     - DNS records

    Can be called from the context menu or network error page.

BUILD
    To build an extension run `make'

SUPPORT
    All issues must be send to
        https://github.com/und3f/checkhost-ext/issues

    Extension's page on AMO
        https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/check-host/
